**Alife**

[On the Liveliness of Artificial Life](https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2302.10196) <br> Koh et al. -- *preprint*

<br>

**Astrobiology**

[Dark microbiome and extremely low organics in Atacama fossil delta unveil Mars life detection limits](https://doi.org/10.1038/s41467-023-36172-1) <br> Azua-Bustos et al. -- *Nature Communications*

[Oxygenic photosynthetic responses of cyanobacteria exposed under an M-dwarf starlight simulator: Implications for exoplanet’s habitability](https://doi.org/10.3389/fpls.2023.1070359) <br> Battistuzzi et al. -- *Frontiers in Plant Science*

[Rock Traits Drive Complex Microbial Communities at the Edge of Life](https://doi.org/10.1089/ast.2022.0062) <br> Coleine et al. -- *Astrobiology*

[Mathematical Model of Antibiotic Resistance Determinants’ Stability Under Space Flight Conditions](https://doi.org/10.1089/ast.2022.0076) <br> Ilyin et al. -- *Astrobiology*

[AOTF based spectro-polarimeter for observing Earth as an Exoplanet](https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2302.10712) <br> Jaiswal et al. -- *preprint*

[Doppler Constraints on Planetary Companions to Nearby Sun-like Stars: An Archival Radial Velocity Survey of Southern Targets for Proposed NASA Direct Imaging Missions](https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2302.10310) <br> Laliotis et al. -- *preprint*

[The Emergence of Astrobiology: A Topic-Modeling Perspective](https://doi.org/10.1089/ast.2022.0122) <br> Malaterre et al. -- *Astrobiology*

[The CARMENES search for exoplanets around M dwarfs. Guaranteed time observations Data Release 1 (2016-2020)](https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2302.10528) <br> Ribas et al. -- *preprint*

[Multiverse Predictions for Habitability: Element Abundances](https://doi.org/10.3390/universe8120651) <br> Sandora et al. -- *Universe*

<br>

**Biochemistry**

[Evolution of enzyme functionality in the flavin-containing monooxygenases](https://doi.org/10.1038/s41467-023-36756-x) <br> Bailleul et al. -- *Nature Communications*

[Early Selection of the Amino Acid Alphabet Was Adaptively Shaped by Biophysical Constraints of Foldability](https://doi.org/10.1021/jacs.2c12987) <br> Makarov et al. -- *Journal of the American Chemical Society*

[Conflicting Models for the Origin of Life](https://doi.org/10.1002/9781119555568) <br> Smoukov et al. -- *book*

<br>

**Biology**

[Entropy, Ecology and Evolution: Toward a Unified Philosophy of Biology](https://doi.org/10.3390/e25030405) <br> Cushman -- *Entropy*

<br>

**Chemistry**

[Origin of Chirality in the Molecules of Life](https://doi.org/10.1021/acsearthspacechem.2c00032) <br> Cowan et al. -- *ACS Earth and Space Chemistry*

<br>

**Mathematical biology**

[The Emergence of Social Hierarchy in Collective Motion of Living Matter](https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2302.10403) <br> Greene et al. -- *preprint*

